          <title>LeBron James returns in Lakers' victory over Grizzlies after 2-game absence</title>
          <description><![CDATA[LOS ANGELES (AP) — LeBron James returned to the Los Angeles Lakers on Sunday night in a 116-10 victory over the Memphis Grizzlies after a two-game break. James is fighting a left foot injury and and was away from the team most of last week because of personal reasons.]]></description>
